description: An analysis of Total Organic Carbons (TOC) tested in sediments and Total Suspended Solids (TSS) in water at the Godineau Swamp. For the project, “Preliminary Assessment of the Ecological Status of the Godineau Swamp, South Trinidad”. The purpose of the water and sediment quality component was to obtain baseline data on water and sediment quality in this wetland, in order to detect changes in quality that may be caused by activities within the wetland.
name: TV_TTO_Trinidad_Godineau_Swamp__ecologicalhealth_TOC_TSS_2002
